<article>
<h1>Abellio ScotRail Privacy Policy</h1>
<div id="block-abellio-franchise-share-buttons" class="block block-abellio-franchise">
<div class="content">
<ul class="sharing">
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.scotrail.co.uk/privacy-policy" class="facebook alt-link-processor-fa alt-link-processor-fa-external-link-square" target="_blank" title="Opens in a new window"><span>Share</span></a></li>
